thorwin.math.geo

Class AxisAngle

  • java.lang.Object
    • thorwin.math.geo.AxisAngle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class AxisAngle
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Representation of a rotation using an axis and angle. The angle's positive direction determined using the right-hand-rule.
